data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT trungtam, tenkho, thoigiankiemke, ngaykiemke, phongtiem_tong, phongtiem_nghi, phongtiem_kiemsang, nhanvien_chinh, nhanvien_phu, khoangcach FROM ksnb_lichkiemke where month(ngaycapnhat) = (@pmThang) and year(ngaycapnhat) = (@pmNam) order by trungtam asc, ngaykiemke desc
